str.id: It looks like the impostor has done some events. These will be displayed on your left panel. Review them and then access the room again.
str.str: 看起来卧底做了一些事情。这显示在左侧面板上。请在检查后再次进入房间。

str.id: The costs will be reflected in the prices of the items in the store
str.str: 成本将体现在商品价格上。

str.id: Remember to keep the door locked with the latch. If you don't, the dolls can come out, alter your tests, and even kill you.
str.str: 记住要用插销锁好门。如果不这样做，人偶可能会出逃，改变测试结果，甚至杀死你。

str.id: You have now accepted the case. Outside of the tutorial, you could abandon the case at any time, but you won't be able to find new cases once you've accepted. With this settled, travel to the location when you're ready.
str.str: 你现已接手此案。除非是在教程之外，否则你随时都可以放弃，但接受后就不能再找新案件了。一切就绪后，准备好就前往目的地吧。

str.id: This is the dolls' room. Here you will see what they have done while you slept. Take a look at them, and then let's go back to the room.
str.str: 这是人偶的房间。在这里，你可以看到他们在你睡觉时做了什么。看一眼他们，然后回到房间。
一颗散发着香气的香草豆。

str.id: Let's go back to the panel and start weeding out suspects who don't match our evidence.
str.str: 回到白板并剔除不符合证据的嫌疑人。

str.id: A white flower with soft petals.
There seems to be no way out
This doll is under effects, wait for the effect to finish to apply another one
str.str: 这个人偶正受到某种效果的影响，等待效果结束才能施加另一个。

str.id: You have all the clues and all the information about the dolls, but this is completely random for each doll.
str.str: 你拥有所有线索和人偶的所有信息，但每个人偶都是完全随机的。

str.id: Multiple targets have appeared in the photo; try to get closer and focus only on the target you want.
str.str: 照片中出现了多个目标；试着靠近目标，只关注可疑的目标。

str.id: The target has not been detected, try to focus more and stay at a specific distance where the entire target can be seen
str.str: The target has not been detected, try to focus more and stay at a specific distance where the entire target can be seen

str.id: The items you equip will be lost!
str.str: 你装备的物品将会丢失！

str.id: We only have 3 left. Let's go to the room to see who has moved and who has been moved.
str.str: 只剩下3个了。去房间看看有谁动了。

str.id: You've made it through the tutorial, you know the basics! To finish the tutorial, go to bed and sleep. You will go to your safe zone. Use the computer to start a game!
str.str: 你已完成教程，了解了游戏基础！前往床上睡觉结束教程，你将进入安全区。使用电脑即可开始游戏！

str.id: You are the guardian of dolls, one of them is alive and intends to kill you. You must discover which one it is before 09:00.
str.str: 你是人偶的看守者，其中有个人偶被恶灵附身，打算杀死你。你必须在09:00之前找出它是谁。

str.id: Perfect, we have 5 suspects left. Let's go to sleep again.
str.str: 很好，还剩下5位嫌疑人。再去睡觉吧。

str.id: Random but endless mode, you have a 3-minute timer to fix the case and there is a leaderboard of leaders
str.str: 随机的无尽模式，你有3分钟来解决案件。该模式有排行榜

str.id: You need to use the book of souls before you save the imposter doll
str.str: 你得先用灵魂之书才能收集卧底人偶

str.id: I've given you a few items to use. Access the chest behind you to retrieve the objects and weapons. Equip all the items, and to use them, switch weapons using the forward or previous weapon change button.
str.str: 我为你准备了一些物品和武器。请前往你背后的箱子拿取。把所有物品都装备上，使用时可以通过前进或后退的武器切换按钮更换武器。

str.id: The standard difficulty for each player, all clues will be made at 08:00, you have the option to see the names of the dolls and the list of actions of the imposter
str.str: 标准的难度，所有线索出现在08:00，你可以选择查看人偶的名字和卧底的行动列表

str.id: It's the last hour. We only have this chance to find out. Let's go to the room.
str.str: 这是最后一小时。只剩这次机会能找出卧底了。前往房间吧。

str.id: Alright, let's discover some things about one of the dolls. We'll choose Lil for this. Apply all the elixirs and cards to her. Open your notebook and take notes on everything you observe. For instance, when you apply an elixir, you have 10 seconds to check her relationship with another doll, so jot down all your observations. Be sure to take a photo of each doll as well; failing to do so will penalize you with 90% of the final reward. See you in 160 seconds!
str.str: 让我们来了解一些关于这些人偶的信息。我们就选择Lil吧。把所有的灵药和卡牌都用在她身上。打开你的笔记本，记录下你观察到的一切。例如，当你使用一种灵药的时候，你有10秒的时间查看她与其他人偶的关系，所以要把所有的观察都记下来。记得要给每个人偶拍照；如果做不到的话，最终奖励会减少90%。160秒后见！

str.id: I've given you a Soul Book. If you haven't finished the tasks, you can do so now. This book will awaken the impostor, and you have 180 seconds to find the impostor once you use it. If you don't succeed, the impostor will kill you. When you're sure who the impostor is, use the sports bag to trap them inside. The tutorial ends here—it's now up to you to continue and uncover the truth. Good luck!
str.str: 我给了你一本灵魂之书。如果你还没完成任务，现在就可以开始了。这本书会唤醒卧底，使用后，你有180秒的时间来找出他。如果你没有成功找到，卧底就会杀了你。当你确定了卧底的身份时，用运动包将其困住。教程到此为止，剩下的就靠你自己去揭开真相了。祝你好运！

str.id: Welcome to Career Mode. In this game mode, you will need to uncover information about the dolls and solve each case correctly.
str.str: 欢迎来到生涯模式。在此模式中，你需要揭示人偶的信息，并正确地解开每个案件。.

str.id: You will have a detective role in which you will have to determine, based on the impostor's likes and dislikes listed on the panel to your left, what he likes and doesn't like, who his enemies, friends, loves, or hated individuals are.
str.str: 你将扮演侦探，根据左侧面板上列出的卧底信息，确定人偶的偏好，谁是他的敌人、朋友、爱人或仇人。

str.id: You've used everything you needed to use here.
str.str: 你用完了这里所需的全部东西。

str.id: You're short of ingredients to make this
Only suitable for professionals, it starts at 08:00 and only has 3 effective clues, there are no photos or aids, some of the data is hidden, you have limited access to the map
str.str: 适合专家游玩的难度，开始于08:00，只有3条有效线索，没有照片或帮助，隐藏一些数据，能探索的地图空间有限

str.id: Let's set a trap for the impostor. We already know that he likes TV and music. Turn on the lights.
str.str: 让我们给卧底设个陷阱。我们知道他喜欢电视和音乐。打开灯吧。

str.id: You've broken your new record with {new} nights! of the {old} nights before!
str.str: 你以{new}夜的成绩，打破了先前{old}夜的记录！

str.id: You can try it now in PC
str.str: 你现在可以用电脑进行尝试

str.id: Electricity On! Head back to the house.
You've unlocked a new extra mode!
str.str: 你解锁了新的额外模式！

str.id: Random mode but in race mode with medals
str.str: 随机模式，但可以竞速获得奖牌

str.id: Can you help me with a positive review?

Welcome to the refuge! This is your safe zone. Here, you can start a new game on the computer, view your collection of dolls and trophies, and also customize this place by clicking on the colour palette icon on your desktop!
str.str: 欢迎来到避难所！这是你的安全区。你可以在电脑上开始新游戏，查看人偶和奖杯收藏，并点击桌面上的调色板图标来自定义这地方！

str.id: Activate the final battle to uncover the impostor.
str.str: 激活最后的战斗，揭穿卧底伪装。

str.id: A small, dark, and shriveled heart.
str.str: 一颗小小的阴暗枯萎之心。

str.id: To sleep, simply point at the bed and click on it.
str.str: 指向并点击床即可睡觉。

str.id: You have lost 90% of the entire reward due to missing photos.
str.str: 由于缺失照片，你损失了90%的奖励。

str.id: One more step of difficulty, there are no extra clues, You can't see the names or list
str.str: 更上一层的难度，没有额外线索，你看不到名字或列表

str.id: Review the various tabs to get familiar with them. When you're ready, click the Accept button to take on this case.
str.str: 浏览各个标签了解内容。准备好后，点击接受按钮接手案件。

str.id: Only visible items that you can equip
str.str: 只有你可以装备的可见物品

str.id: To start, there are 20 dolls. Check them on the board and when you are ready, go to the room to meet them.
str.str: 一开始有20个人偶。先在白板上查看它们，准备好之后，就去房间与它们见面。

str.id: Go to sleep and let's see if the clue is solved in the next hour.
str.str: 去睡觉吧，看看在下一个小时能否找到线索。

str.id: It is clear that he likes blood. It could be either of the two, but check the boxes. Freddy is missing and his box is full of blood. He left this verdict for you. When you are sure, discard the candidate.
str.str: 很明显他喜欢血。可能是两者中的任何一个，但你得检查那些盒子。弗莱迪不见了，而他的盒子里满是血。当你确定后，就可以排除这个嫌疑人了。

str.id: Portable device that produces a flame to start a fire.
str.str: 可以产生火焰的便携点火装置。

str.id: He has fallen into our trap and turned off the lights. We can now discard all those who like the light.
str.str: 他中了我们的圈套，把灯关掉了。我们现在可以排除所有喜欢光明的人。

str.id: Take doll photos for fill the clues
str.str: 拍摄人偶照片填补线索

str.id: Enter the house and find the dolls' room. Use the flashlight to see better.
str.str: 进入房屋，找到人偶的房间。用手电筒能看得更清楚。

str.id: Take notes on the behavior of the dolls
You can't make this, it doesn't fit any recipe
Remember that you won't be able to interact with anything right now since this is the tutorial. Now, let's turn on the electricity. Equip your fuse and go to the back of the house to activate it.
str.str: 记得这只是教程，你还不能真正操作任何东西。现在，让我们开始通电吧。装上保险丝，然后去房子后面启动电源。

str.id: Expert mode, you start from 06:00, there are no extra clues and no photographs
str.str: 专家模式，从06:00开始，没有额外线索，也没有照片

str.id: If you return to the safehouse, the house will restore its state and you will lose the equipped items
str.str: 如果你回到安全屋，房子将恢复原状，你将失去装备

str.id: As you unlock new levels, new ones will appear!
str.str: 解锁新关卡后，会出现新的人偶！

str.id: You have lost 75% for not discovering the impostor
str.str: 未能找出卧底，损失75%的奖励

str.id: The lower the ratio, the more information about the dolls will be released initially (from 2 to 10)
str.str: 比率越低，初始公开的人偶信息越多（范围2-10）。

str.id: You will have a case available with various dynamic parameters. It will display information like the current one, and if you don't like it, you can search for a new case in exchange for money. Currently, in tutorial mode, we have limited your interactions; you won't be able to buy, craft, exit the case, or search for a new case.
str.str: 您将获得一个案件，其中包含多种动态参数。它会显示类似当前案件的信息，如果不满意，您可以用钱换取新的案件。现在，在教程模式中，我们对您的操作进行了限制；您暂时无法购买、制作、退出或者寻找新案件。

str.id: We have Ricky on the couch and Monty at the piano, so we already have the 2 possible candidates. However, we are not going to take the 50% risk. Let's go back to the room to rule out the one that can't be and wait for his next event.
str.str: Ricky在沙发上，Monty在钢琴旁，所以我们有了两个可能的人选。不过我们不会去冒那50%的风险。回到房间，排除那个不可能的人选，然后等待他的下一次行动，从而确认人选。

str.id: You've got {new} nights, you haven't managed to beat your record of {old} nights
str.str: 你度过了{new}晚，没能打破之前的{old}晚记录
和朋友一起玩旋转木马
